<item>
            <title>[LU-116] fix mmp test 10 to allow e2fsck run on mounted filesystem with -n option</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-116</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The e2fsck in the latest e2fsprogs version 1.41.12.2.ora1 could be run on mounted filesystem with -n option specified. The mmp test 10 needs to be fixed to verify this and check the e2fsck return value properly.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
