&lt;p&gt;The test logs were uploaded to Maloo by maloo_upload.sh. However, I could not see them on &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com&lt;/a&gt;. I also tried to manually upload the mmp.tar.gz through the &quot;upload results&quot; web page but the results still did not show up.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;John, could you please take a look at this issue? Thanks a lot in advance.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
